{"tid":1972212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"購不合格中國口罩惹議    芬蘭官員請辭","createTime":"2020-04-14T11:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T02:21:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"50ad5f960e3b3dab22c4880d4e2b73f51c582627","tid":1972212,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/m_fVROdk2RYHuXFjrF9rWQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/124f0420-7d52-11ea-bd15-3e7d6fd59b84\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fm_fVROdk2RYHuXFjrF9rWQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-04%2F124f0420-7d52-11ea-bd15-3e7d6fd59b84&h=7b4741ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n芬蘭政府向中國採購逾200萬個口罩運抵當地，經檢測發現不符當地標準，不適宜在醫院使用，事件引起極大爭議。負責採購物資的芬蘭國家應急物資儲備中心主管內洛馬（Tomi Lounema）日前請辭，成為該國自疫情以來首名辭職的政府官員。<br />\n<br />\n芬蘭媒體報道，內洛馬承認該批物資是以共1000萬歐元（約8400萬港元）向2名商人訂購，其中一人是從事高利貸的商人薩瑪斯特（Onni Sarmaste），另一人則是有金融犯罪前科的電視真人騷演員耶爾哈（Tiina Jylh&auml;）。據知，國家應急物資儲備中心已向薩瑪斯特支付全部交易金額，並向耶爾哈支付半數約250萬歐元，目前已被銀行凍結。<br />\n<br />\n芬蘭勞工部長哈塔寧（Tuula Haatainen）在上周五（10日）的記者會上表示，她事前不知有關交易，直到媒體報道事件。她指此事嚴重打擊國家應急物資儲備中心的信譽，而洛內馬已提出辭職並獲准。芬蘭國家應急物資儲備中心隸屬勞工部，負責與芬蘭政府指定的相關公司協調管理儲備國家應急物資。<br />\n<br />\n涉事口罩經檢測後顯示未達在芬蘭醫院使用的標準，只能用於居家看護設施，或看護者上門探望病人。洛內馬當時解釋，中國口罩市場極度混亂，價格持續上漲，當局必須迅速訂購及預先付款，因此商業風險非常高，又指其他歐洲國家也遇到類似問題。中國外交部其後回應指，有關物資沒以醫用口罩名義向中方申報出口，呼籲外界沒查清前不要輕易下結論。"},{"pid":"fac3bbd33e3c0d0eef6ac3749afcdf28816b814d","tid":1972212,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ad1a5c8f3d1da17b4cbcc413a57cc88ed2d01c","tid":1972212,"uid":70786,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:31:56.000Z","msg":"真係勁<br />\n呃完人錢有中方出嚟開脫責任<br />\n錢就袋袋平安入共產黨袋"},{"pid":"fdc5799776bba2753be9a1e55a222ad180b977e4","tid":1972212,"uid":173271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:42:32.000Z","msg":"全部MIC的話果1000萬凍過水了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bb3374461b6dab4cb0af86a313d76c25da18ad","tid":1972212,"uid":286792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:50:18.000Z","msg":"感謝黨送病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後仲賣貴價垃圾級別口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3b9a983f1d9a902fe3c0a916b363d39a8a13c3","tid":1972212,"uid":182701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"8400萬買200萬個支那制口罩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b998e78ed6980185ed27c243f726d78745926622","tid":1972212,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T19:35:08.000Z","msg":"點解唔搵台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁傻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743cd436bf2d6cc61f4fb36961d2bd08fbd08cf8","tid":1972212,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T19:36:50.000Z","msg":"出條法例禁中國貨入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1cf3db45070b48b6dcc56b0919e496e6ccab1e","tid":1972212,"uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T19:39:15.000Z","msg":"其中一人是從事高利貸的商人薩瑪斯特（Onni Sarmaste），另一人則是有金融犯罪前科的電視真人騷演員耶爾哈（Tiina Jylh&auml;）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cla